{"tid":1747453,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港台一名兼職女記者被控參與暴動","createTime":"2019-11-23T08:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T09:14:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0a1b0503e33128f9987832b74f2e4d74922bb3dc","tid":1747453,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"二十歲被告朱梓瑩本身是嶺大學生，在港台任職兼職記者，她被控於周一晚與二十三歲運輸工人柯俊明，在油麻地彌敦道近窩打老道交界與其他人參與暴動，兩人毋須答辯，裁判官批准二人保釋，案件押後至明年三月十九日，期間不可離境，要交出旅遊證件及遵守晚十一朝七的宵禁令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/561781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F561781&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=91e0ecc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F561781&h=04483b57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/561781</a>"},{"pid":"3d12857bf1a113ff555021b1dffab5c2dd78c9d4","tid":1747453,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:23:19.000Z","msg":"擺明記者先玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b813f39f9d18a4073667063f2324ce8ebd94c9","tid":1747453,"uid":125026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:23:31.000Z","msg":"咁on9"},{"pid":"f454d32d9c4f5cab3f5b2ccf0962fa87f5f822df","tid":1747453,"uid":58896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:26:37.000Z","msg":"On99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如將嗰日<br />\n由太子到尖東一帶嘅所有人<br />\n（咪撚漏居民旅客）<br />\n全部起訴<br />\n<br />\n唔撚洗煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.